You can set the default radius with this command if you insert numeric value after this word:

Examples:
---------------
<b>radius:3
radius:5
radius:10
radius:50</b>

The numeric value after the radius is the distance from you in kilimeters.

Remove your personal radius settings:
<b>radius:reset</b>

Show all your current settings:
<b>setting:show</b>

Please use /help if you need more information.